Mourners in Ruiru- Kiambu county are  preparing to bid goodbye to a family after three of its last surviving members were killed in a fatal road accident at Kinungi area when a speeding motorist rammed into their vehicle head on.
The late Peter Kimani Gikonyo, his wife Zipporah Muthoni and their son David died barely 4 weeks  after burying their daughter who died after a short illness. 